		div#header
			div.row.fullWidth
				div.small-12.columns.hero
					div.row
						div.tagline.small-12.medium-8.medium-centered.columns
							h1 Streamline Your Contribution Process with Carbon
					div.row
						div.register.small-12.medium-3.medium-centered.columns
							a.button.expand.radius(href="{% url 'sponsorship:register' %}") REGISTER
		div#features
			div.row.feature
				div.medium-12.columns
					h2#intro Carbon helps nonprofits manage fundraising campaigns
						br
						| by providing a platform to engage financial and
						br
						| in-kind contributors.
			div.row.feature
				div.medium-3.medium-offset-1.small-12.columns
					div.image
						img(src="{{STATIC_URL}}images/icn_1.jpg")
				div.medium-7.small-12.columns
					div.description
						div.title
							h3 Instant Communication
						div.text
							| Easily broadcast sponsor forms and donation requests while maintaining contributor lists for future outreach.
